  "_comment": "AI Workflow settings — schema v0.4 (v0.6 CLI automation layer). hybrid mode: Cowork desktop for Stage 1 Sonnet + CLI agent team Opus for Stages 2–13. CLI 실행: claude --teammate-mode tmux",
